oratenoblepdf  httpwwwstanleygibbonscomimagessgcorporateprmpacquisitionvpdf  httpwwwstanleygibbonscomimagessgcorporatemallettantiquesacquiredbydreweattsandbloomsburypdf  httpwwwantiquestradegazettecomnewsfebstanleygibbonsgroupwinsdealoftheyearawardfornobleacquisition  httpwwwharperscouknewsstanleygibbonsbuysbidforwineonlineauctionplatformarticle  httpwwwthedrinksbusinesscomfinewineprofilebidforwine  phillips stanley stamp collecting a guide to modern philately revised edition stanley gibbons london  p isbn    years of gibbons stamp monthly by michael briggs in gibbons stamp monthly october  pp–  stanley gibbons acquires philatelic exporter philatelicexportercom february  retrieved  april  from internet archive  stanley gibbons investments stanley gibbons retrieved    chairmans statement pdf audited results for the year ended  december  stanley gibbons  retrieved    levene tony  stamps are easily licked london the guardian retrieved    levene tony  philately wont get you anywhere london guardian retrieved    litterick david  bloomberg puts stamp on stanley gibbons indices the daily telegraph london   httpwwwantiquestradegazettecomnewsjulstanleygibbonsbuyonlinewineauctioneer  stanley gibbons group ltd audited results for the year ended  december  pdf  retrieved    httpwwwstanleygibbonsplccomwpcontentuploadsdlmuploadssggroupaccountstomarpdf external linksedit wikimedia commons has media related to stanley gibbons official website authority control worldcat identities viaf  lccn no isni     gnd  retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlestanleygibbonsoldid categories stamp collectingcompanies listed on the london stock exchangecompanies listed on the alternative investment marketbritish royal warrant holdersbritish stamp dealersstanley gibbonshidden categories cs maint unfit urlpages using deprecated image syntaxofficial website different in wikidata and wikipediawikipedia articles with viaf identifierswikipedia articles with lccn identifierswikipedia articles wit