nsel for hewlettpackard and compaq computer corp where he managed both companies international legal operations jim started his career in technology with digital equipment where he was responsible for litigation compliance and antitrust activities jim holds a juris doctor degree and a master’s degree in public policy from the university of michigan as well as a bachelor’s degree from northern michigan university products – stanley michael distinguished jewels  cart log in or create an account home  products  page  of  products browse all items bulgari frontpage h stern kieselstein cord vintage sort by featured price low to high price high to low alphabetically az alphabetically za date old to new date new to old best selling s gold diamond ruby enamel snake bracelet   sold out s tiffany  co angela cummings gold rose petal earrings   sold out s arthur king gold diamond pearl earrings   sold out s italian gold diamond cocktail ring   s tiffany  co gold rose petal earrings   s tiffany  co gold virgo zodiac pendant necklace   sold out s angela cummings gold turquoise mosaic earrings   s kieselstein cord gold alligator cufflinks   sold out s tiffany  co angela cummings coral hematite onyx gold bracelet   s tiffany  co paloma picasso amethyst bracelet   s tiffany  co angela cummings gold lapis checkered earrings   adorable gold ruby diamond onyx vintage car brooch pin   sold out page  of  next hand tools  hand tools sets  stanley tools menu search enter a product to get the results to choose from submit enter a product to get the results to choose from submit find a retailer mystanley mystanley account sign in email address password submit forgot password join mystanley join the mystanley community to rate and review stanley® tools receive special offers and learn about new stanley® products sign up hi  edit profile not  sign out english country united states language select a language english hand tools trusted hand tools – working for you browse by category screwdrivers