uilds tension with slow piano sparse acoustic guitar resonant synthesizer and steady drum parts rock and roll man is a conscious attempt to add a footstomper to the album and stanley forces his sneering vocals luckily walsh redeems things with a piercing guitar solo moving right along is decent folkrock enhanced by organ flute and guitar solos a radically altered arrangement of bob dylans subterranean homesick blues closes the album stanley would release one more solo album before forming the michael stanley band and becoming a superstar in ohio but it all began with the uneven yet promising michael stanley  bret adams radio days s rock cd  on sale add to cart michael stanley you break it you bought it cd  add to cart michael stanley msb cd  add to cart   michael stanley live in tangiers the acoustic shows cd  add to cart michael stanley in a very short time cd  add to cart michael stanley heartland cd  add to cart   michael stanley north coast cd  add to cart   michael stanley solo years  cd  add to cart michael stanley live at the ritz nyc  cd  add to cart michael stanley you cant fight fashion cd  add to cart   the abones not now cd  super savings add to cart bryan adams bryan adams cd  super savings add to cart    off bryan adams icon cd  super savings add to cart   bryan adams live live live cd  add to cart   bryan adams reckless cd  add to cart   alan price savaloy dip cd  add to cart the allman brothers gold cd  super savings add to cart   the allman brothers live at the atlanta international pop festival cd  super savings add to cart    off the allman brothers peakin at the beacon cd  on sale add to cart   gregg allman  various artists all my friends celebrating the songs  voice of gregg cd  super savings add to cart music lovers ratings  reviews be the first music lover to write an online review of this product similar products genre pop  rock music categories oldies rock n roll get email alerts for michael stanley join  fans product info upc  shipping weig